Ent Gandalf Fellowship and Moria Swarm
shadow.</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Cards</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Starting:<br />
Frodo, RA<br />
The One Ring, RR<br />
<br />
Pippin, MT<br />
Merry, FOtB<br />
Quickbeam (Can play if you flip Merry and Pippin 1st.)<br />
<br />
Adventure: <br />
Like in my last beginner deck, I let the<br />
beginner chose what site path to use.<br />
Make sure, though, to use King Sites.<br />
<br />
